cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel neural network architecture for machine translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of recurrent neural networks. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves the use of neural networks for sequence modeling, which is a common technique in computer vision.
